dfischer.utils

Class PrxJob

  • java.lang.Object
    • dfischer.utils.PrxJob

  • public class PrxJob
extends java.lang.Object
    Allows the PrxJob utility to be called directly from a Java program (Professional Edition only). For further information about the PrxJob utility see "Application Reference Manual".
